---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <p>At CampSoon (www.campsoon.com), user digital security is an uncompromising pillar of our architecture. Our custom browser utilities handle user queries strictly on local storage runtime configurations.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>No Account Access Exploit:</strong> We never harvest, capture, or store passwords, credentials, or private keys relating to official park reservation accounts.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Gateways Protection:</strong> Financial transaction processing layers are fully handled under PCI-DSS standards by Stripe. No clear text card details ever interface with our web hosts.</li>
      <li><strong>Data Queries:</strong> Direct all corporate transparency data logs requests cleanly to support@campsoon.com.</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
